HEADWORD: Masthead
<hw>Mast"head"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>To cause
to go to the masthead as a punishment.</def>
<rj><au>Marryat.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

